Poundland has posted annual sales exceeding the £ 1billion mark for the first time .
The company began as a single shop in Burton-on-Trent 25 years ago , has become Europe 's largest single-price discount retailer .
The firm revealed yesterday total revenue over the 12-month period - excluding its Spain interests - grew 11.8 per cent to just over £ 1.1 billion , breaking through £ 1bn barrier , with a trial expansion into Spain .